OL,3,CStarmer says Fifa 'wrong' to ban
OL,4,Creusable water bottles at World Cup
OL,5,Cstadiums
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister has said Fifa's ban
OL,8,Fon bringing refillable water bottles
OL,9,Finto World Cup stadiums is "just
OL,10,Fwrong" and asked Fifa to "think of the
OL,11,Ffans".
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer said that the
OL,14,Ffootball governing body should rethink
OL,15,Fthe change in policy and condemned the
OL,16,Fmove, saying it was "about making
OL,17,Fmoney".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
