PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780733118
OL,3,CStarmer says Fifa 'wrong' to ban
OL,4,Creusable water bottles at World Cup
OL,5,Cstadiums
OL,7,FFifa says the decision is to "prevent
OL,8,Frisk and injury to players and
OL,9,Fattendees", but it has led to concerns
OL,10,Fover fans' welfare in the extreme heat
OL,11,Fof the North American summer.
OL,13,FThe previous policy for ticket holders
OL,14,Fhad allowed an empty, transparent,
OL,15,Freusable bottle with up to one litre
OL,16,Fcapacity to be brought in, but as
OL,17,Ffirst reported by The Athletic, an
OL,18,Fupdate issued on June 2 confirmed that
OL,19,Freusable bottles are no longer
OL,20,Fpermitted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780733118
OL,3,CStarmer says Fifa 'wrong' to ban
OL,4,Creusable water bottles at World Cup
OL,5,Cstadiums
OL,7,FBottled water cost between four and
OL,8,Fsix US dollars (#3-#4.50) at last
OL,9,Fsummer's Club World Cup, which took
OL,10,Fplace in the US.
OL,12,FA keen football fan himself, the PM
OL,13,Fsaid the policy will put even more
OL,14,Ffinancial strain on fans, who are
OL,15,Falready "spending a fortune" on
OL,16,Ftickets and travel.
OL,18,FHe told LBC on Friday that it was
OL,19,F"just wrong" and criticised the ticket
OL,20,Fprice, saying they are "far too
OL,21,Fexpensive".
OL,26,@wD@IOUwD@\O]
