OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780733118
OL,3,CStarmer says Fifa 'wrong' to ban
OL,4,Creusable water bottles at World Cup
OL,5,Cstadiums
OL,7,FStarmer added: "I would call on Fifa
OL,8,Fto just look again at this. Think
OL,9,Fabout it. Think of the fans."
OL,11,FIn May, academics at World Weather
OL,12,FAttribution (WWA) expressed concern
OL,13,Fabout the impact of extreme heat on
OL,14,Fplayer and fan welfare, with
OL,15,Fsupporters said to be especially
OL,16,Fvulnerable.
OL,18,FWWA expects nine of the 104 World Cup
OL,19,Fmatches to be played at a Wet Bulb
OL,20,FGlobe Temperature (WBGT) above 26
OL,21,Fdegrees.
OL,26,@oD@POU
