OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FA Fifa spokesperson said: "Fifa is
OL,17,Fcommitted to protecting the health and
OL,18,Fsafety of all players, referees, fans,
OL,19,Fvolunteers and staff.
