OL,3,CStarmer says Fifa 'wrong' to ban
OL,4,Creusable water bottles at World Cup
OL,5,Cstadiums
OL,7,F"Outside bottles are already
OL,8,Fprohibited at several of these venues
OL,9,Ffor safety considerations and Fifa is
OL,10,Fapplying this consideration across its
OL,11,Ftournament stadiums.
OL,13,F"Fifa works closely with each host
OL,14,Fcity committee and local authorities
OL,15,Fon heat mitigation factors for fans
OL,16,Ftravelling to the stadium, which can
OL,17,Finclude resources such as misting
OL,18,Fstations, fans, hydration stations,
OL,19,Fcooling tents and more around the
OL,20,Fstadium footprint.
